channel.title: Aristoi | Looking for developers
channel.description:
[center][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/7vgxzeL.png[/img]
We are currently looking for two Java/Python (either) programmers to undertake a serious and professional pre-hd emulation of RuneScape using the Emulous framework.
If you feel you could contribute positively to the project, please leave your preffered method of contact below and we will get back to you as soon as possible.
Thanks for your time,
The Aristoi Team[/center]
